snippet.title: Ghost Recon Wildlands Narco Road Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover Narco Road, Ghost Recon Wildlands first expansion. Your mission will be to infiltrate various gangs led by El Invisible, a mysterious master of drug smuggling.  

You’ll face new challenges all along the way.
With race cars, monster trucks, choppers, gold plated guns…
